|name=Kamezuka Kofun
|image=
|location=[[Nakanoto, Ishikawa|Nakanoto]], {{ill|Kashima District, Ishikawa|ja|鹿島郡|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Ishikawa Prefecture|ja|石川県|qq=draft}}
